description:
Katherine Heigl [Gray’s Anatomy, Knocked Up, 27 Dresses] and Sarah Chalke [Scrubs, Rick and Morty, Roseanne, How I Met Your Mother] join Anna to talk about their new Netflix show Firefly Lane, adaptation, lifetime friendships, award shows, fame, embarrassing moments, planting apple orchards and more. Later in the episode OBG/YN Dr. Jen Gunter is back to answer questions and give some qualified advice. 

Learn more about Dr. Gunter and her book The Vagina Bible at her website drjengunter.com

Upstart Find out how Upstart can lower your monthly payments today when you go to upstart.com/ANNA.  Loan amounts will be determined based on your credit, income, and certain other information provided in your loan application.
